00389         public:
00391             const bool Sort(
00392                     const int (*cmp)(const T&, const T&)    
00393 
00394                     )
00395             {
00396                 bool b_Result = true;
00397                 if (GetCount() < 2)
00398                 {
00399                     b_Result = true;
00400                 }
00401                 else
00402                 {
00403                     // Get a reference element.
00404                     T t_Ref = RemoveTail();
00405 
00406                     // Dispatch elements in q_1 and q_2.
00407                     Queue<T> q_1(0), q_2(0);
00408                     while (! IsEmpty())
00409                     {
00410                         T t_Sort = RemoveTail();
00411                         if (cmp(t_Sort, t_Ref) > 0)
00412                         {
00413                             q_1.AddTail(t_Sort);
00414                         }
00415                         else
00416                         {
00417                             q_2.AddTail(t_Sort);
00418                         }
00419                     }
00420 
00421                     // Sort each list q_1 and q_2
00422                     if (q_1.Sort(cmp) && q_2.Sort(cmp))
00423                     {
00424                         // Eventually restore q_1...
00425                         b_Result = true;
00426                         for (   Iterator it_1 = q_1.GetIterator();
00427                                 q_1.IsValid(it_1);
00428                                 q_1.MoveNext(it_1))
00429                         {
00430                             if (! AddTail(q_1.GetAt(it_1)))
00431                             {
00432                                 b_Result = false;
00433                             }
00434                         }
00435                         // ... then the reference element...
00436                         if (! AddTail(t_Ref))
00437                         {
00438                             b_Result = false;
00439                         }
00440                         // ... and then q_2.
00441                         for (   Iterator it_2 = q_2.GetIterator();
00442                                 q_2.IsValid(it_2);
00443                                 q_2.MoveNext(it_2))
00444                         {
00445                             if (! AddTail(q_2.GetAt(it_2)))
00446                             {
00447                                 b_Result = false;
00448                             }
00449                         }
00450                     }
00451                 }
00452                 return b_Result;
00453             }
